   Jacquemyn, Hans; Gielen, Marie, Katholieke Univ Leuven, Biol Dept, Plant Conservat \& Populat Biol, Kasteelpk Arenberg 31, BE-3001 Heverlee, Belgium.
   Brys, Rein, Res Inst Forest \& Nat, Geraardsbergen, Belgium.},
