Abstract = {The seed production of hand pollinated flowers indicates that distylous
   C. flava (A. Nels.) Payson is both intramorph and self-compatible. In
   addition, there is no inhibition of pollen tube growth following either
   intramorph or self-pollinations. Despite the potential for crosses
